name: Pardon My Fro Silk Duster
description: Elevate your daily outfits effortlessly with this stylish satin topper, suitable for any occasion - from casual outings to lounging at home. This versatile piece complements all body shapes and serves as the ideal layering essential to showcase your style. Stand out in this luxurious silk duster and experience the compliments rolling in!

bullet_2: The long sleeves provide a touch of sophistication, while the self-fabric tie belt cinches at the waist, offering a flattering silhouette for all body shapes.
bullet_3: Whether tied up for a sleek, polished look or left open for a casual, flowy vibe, this duster adapts to your mood and setting.
bullet_4: The meticulous design features belt loops and inside ties, ensuring a secure closure that moves with you, guaranteeing both style and comfort are never compromised.
bullet_5: The side slits and straight hemline further enhance the duster's effortless drape, offering generous room for movement without sacrificing on style.

name: Pardon My Fro Chiffon Duster
description: Elevate everyday moments with Pardon My Fro Dusters, the epitome of grace wrapped in the vibrant essence of Afrocentric artistry! A Tapestry of Culture: Each duster is a masterful fusion of design and narrative, paying homage to the rich tapestry of African culture. Be the vibrant masterpiece amidst monotones, making an unapologetic statement wherever you go.

name: Pardon My Fro Women's Trench Coat
description: Stay ahead of the fashion curve with Pardon My Fro Trench Coats, where chic meets unparalleled comfort! Our coats encapsulate the art of bold self-expression, enabling you to step out with confidence and flair, making every sidewalk your runway. Drenched in Artistry: Immerse yourself in the striking, artistic prints that breathe life into these exceptional coats. Each design, inspired by the eclectic and vibrant spirit of Afrocentric culture, tells a compelling story of heritage, strength, and elegance. With Pardon My Fro, your outerwear is not just apparel, it's a canvas. Crafted for You: Quality and comfort are non-negotiable. Every trench is meticulously crafted with precision, ensuring not just a garment, but an experience. The fabric whispers against your skin with gentleness, while the sturdy construction promises longevity. It's an investment in your statement style. Stand Out Unapologetically: Why blend in when you were born to stand out? Slip into a Pardon My Fro Trench Coat and let the world see you in all your unparalleled glory. It's more than a coat, it's a celebration of your unyielding spirit and unique identity.
bullet_1: Solid windbreaker fabrication with printed mesh border.
bullet_2: Semi-fitted: somewhat close to the body, but cut for ease of movement and fabric drape.
bullet_3: Lightweight, double-breasted style with gold buttons and belted waistline.
bullet_4: Large, oversized hood and nitch collar
bullet_5: Long sleeves with gold button cuffs
